$0000ffff constant TIM2_PSC_PSC                                     \ PSC[15:0]: Prescaler value The counter clock frequency (CK_CNT) is equal to fCK_PSC / (PSC[15:0] + 1). PSC contains the value to be loaded in the active prescaler register at each update event (including when the counter is cleared through UG bit of TIMx_EGR register or through trigger controller when configured in 'reset mode').


